<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٧٧٦ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">ابْنُ جَعْفَرٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا عَدْوَى وَلَا طِيَرَةَ، وَيُعْجِبُنِي الْفَأْلُ،<span class="c5"> قَالُوا:</span> وَمَا الْفَأْلُ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> كَلِمَةٌ طَيِّبَةٌ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>